# Techshift Website — Project Overview

**Stack:** Astro 6 · Tailwind CSS 4 (CSS-first, no config file) · React + Framer Motion · Cloudflare Pages · TypeScript strict

## Quality Bar

Every change must satisfy all five:
1. **Aesthetic** — editorial layouts, generous whitespace, intentional type, purposeful motion
2. **SEO** — single `<h1>`, structured data, meta tags, alt text
3. **AEO** — direct answers first, named entities, FAQ schema, `llms.txt` updated
4. **Performance** — minimal client JS, optimised images, LCP < 2.5 s
5. **Accessibility** — keyboard nav, 4.5:1 contrast, 44 px touch targets, focus rings, `prefers-reduced-motion`

## Section Template

```html
<section id="section-id" class="bg-surface-{variant} py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24" aria-labelledby="section-heading">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1280px] px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-12">
    <!-- content -->
  </div>
</section>
```

Container is always `max-w-[1280px]` with responsive horizontal padding.

## When Adding a New Section

1. Add HTML in `src/pages/index.astro` at the right position
2. Wrap in `<AnimatedSection client:visible>` for scroll reveal
3. Update `src/pages/llms.txt.ts` and `src/pages/llms-full.txt.ts`
4. If it contains Q&A content, add to `faqItems` for FAQPage schema
